rows.label: bf10100100_0010
rows.name:
This place looks like it was once a city,
and quite an old one at that.

rows.label: bf10100100_0020
rows.name: It's actually a lot like the stuff we saw in Mors...

rows.label: bf10100100_0030
rows.name:
Way more dusty, though.
Maybe because it's so dry up here.

rows.label: bf10100100_0050
rows.name: It seems to have been a child's vehicle.

rows.label: bf10100100_0070
rows.name:
So that means...
People lived here, once.

rows.label: bf10100100_0080
rows.name: It must've been a grand old city.

rows.label: bf10100100_0090
rows.name: It stretches further than the eye can see...

rows.label: bf10100100_0100
rows.name:
You could fit...the entire population of
Alst into this place, and with room to spare...
